n</span><br>  Posts: 1<br> <font color=#333333>(1/3/03 2:54:52 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub102.ezboard.com/fthemagicianstowerspells.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=1747.topic>Reply</a>    <br>ezSupporter<br> </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Summoned weapons?</span><hr size=1> I was wondering if anyone might be so kind as to give me a quick breakdown of what spells at what levels summon weapons, and any other info about them you can offer.  <br>
<br>
It's not that I'm lazy.  I've gone through the spell list, but there's SOOO many mage summoned items, I'm sure I missed a few.  All I saw was a level 29 spell to summon some 7/27 1hs, and another one at like level 63.  Just want to know what other levels have spells that summon weapons for pets.  I basically want to PL a mage up to summon weapons for my enc/shaman.  Thanks in advance. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#989dca><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub102.ezboard.com/bthemagicianstower.showUserPublicProfile?gid=whammydill>Whammydill</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Magician</span><br>  Posts: 21<br> <font color=#333333>(1/3/03 3:20:33 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub102.ezboard.com/fthemagicianstowerspells.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=1747.topic&index=1>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: Summoned weapons?</span><hr size=1> well, if you're sole intention is just to summon weapons, you will be missing out on things the mage can offer, but thats not the issue.  <br>
<br>
I will try to break them down.  The level, the spell, and the prduct.<br>
<br>
1. Summon Dagger =  Magic 3/21 dagger<br>
8. Staff of Tracing = 7/40 2hb 1 charge of FLARE<br>
12. Summon Fang = 5/26 piercer<br>
16. Staff of Warding = 8/38 2hb 5 charges of GAZE<br>
20. Spear of Warding = 6/27 piercer +5 CR/FR<br>
24. Staff of Runes = 9/36 2hb 1 charge of CANCEL MAGIC<br>
29 Sword of Runes = 7/27 1hs eff:WARD SUMMONED<br>
34. Staff of Symbols = 10/34 2hb 4 charges of SEE INVISIBLE<br>
39 Dagger of Symbols = 5/20 piercer +5 DR/MR/PR<br>
61 Blade of Walnan = 10/20 1hs +3 Magic DMG +50hp eff: WRATH OF WIND<br>
62. Fist of Ixiblat = 10/20 h2h +3 Fire DMG +50hp eff:WRATH OF FIRE<br>
63. Blade of the Kedge = 10/20 1hs +3 Cold DMG +50hp eff: WRATH OF ICE<br>
<br>
Thats a comprehensive list of our summoned weapons.  However I have omitted the mod-rods, and summoned range weapons.  I would also like to point out the summoned armor and shield we can make.  I suggest you go to lucy.fnord.net and look at the magician spells for more detailed info.<br>
<br>
<br>
