47.topic&index=9>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   pets</span><hr size=1> Pets don't start dual wielding until the mid 20s i think and even then mage pets don't need to have items in both hands to 'dual wield'.<br>
<br>
